  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>To use this technique, the target must be of a size category no larger than you, and must have made an armed melee attack against you since your last turn. You must also have both hands free. Initiate a grapple attempt against the target, which does not provoke an attack of opportunity. If successful, you may immediately make a second grapple check to pin the target.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The first step allows you to use this technique even if the target has not recently attacked you.<br><br>The third step allows you to use the technique with only a single hand free.<br><br>The fourth step allows you to reduce to perform time to an attack action once per day.<br><br>The fifth step allows you to use this technique against creatures up to one size category larger than you.</p>\n",
